{"tid":1936253,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保羅費拉拿：C朗有力踢到40歲","createTime":"2020-03-21T06:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T07:21:34.000Z","uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1bef7a318789346fe2a24e9c54a52997ea175a","tid":1936253,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"意大利《都靈體育報》早前報道，祖雲達斯準備向基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）提供一份直至2024年的新合約，如果事成，這位球王將會至少踢到39歲。 <br />\n<br />\n保羅費拉拿（Paulo Ferreira）於球員時代跟C朗做過6年葡萄牙國家隊隊友，他說：「我認識C朗很久了。他的態度非常專業，一直很努力，相信在身體許可的情況下，他都會保持這個高水準，我認為還有4、5年。」 <br />\n<br />\n現任車路士外借球員技術教練的保羅費拉拿指，C朗已經35歲了，但仍然踢出這樣的表現，證明他好好照顧自己的身體，飲食及休息都得宜，「他仍然是受人尊敬的重要球員，而且大家都害怕他那改變戰局的能力。」"},{"pid":"7cb20f00d1d56f319af70a6a3aa1c5c31b0cb6e4","tid":1936253,"uid":8850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"見好就收 唔好做第2個伊巴"},{"pid":"61f0fbe460d5da00f35d4b08b769bd782d087e33","tid":1936253,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cb20f00d1d56f319af70a6a3aa1c5c31b0cb6e4","tid":1936253,"uid":8850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"見好就收 唔好做第2個伊巴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:29:23.000Z","msg":"伊巴有乜問題？"},{"pid":"5a1f524683c7626b064f1945fe7fdbe31ca159ba","tid":1936253,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61f0fbe460d5da00f35d4b08b769bd782d087e33","tid":1936253,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cb20f00d1d56f319af70a6a3aa1c5c31b0cb6e4","tid":1936253,"uid":8850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"見好就收 唔好做第2個伊巴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:29:23.000Z","msg":"伊巴有乜問題？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"去曼聯"},{"pid":"d971845afee81ba3aa6f08459344ecee37158f3b","tid":1936253,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a1f524683c7626b064f1945fe7fdbe31ca159ba","tid":1936253,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{